  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess the safety of soluble beta-glucan (SBG) in combination
      with antibody and chemotherapy treatment in patients with non-Hodgkin-s lymphoma.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
